    <description>When the Study.Expected Study Date__c is populated, send the SMS for the Study Night when the day arrives for the Expected Study Date
https://basecamp.com/2583453/projects/19794483/todos/515671327
Updated Logic to include Scheduled Path for sending the return Instructions
https://basecamp.com/2583453/projects/19794483/todos/515687396
Add Logic For Non-Traditional Provider Account SMS Protocol and Patient Do Not Send Automated SMS
